### 【删】Delete actors [POST]
删除指定条件的玩家。警告：设置条件为"{}"将删除所有玩家！

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "graphql_Exp": "mutation deleteActor($conditions: JSON!) { delete(conditions: $conditions) { message, status, rmCount } } ",
          "graphql_Arg": {
            "conditions": "{\"dbname\": \"actor-testy\"}"
